(
<figureCitation id="130F2A575C0CFFA848FEFBEBFF33FBB1" box="[159,253,1076,1101]" captionStart="FIGURE 3" captionStartId="23.[151,250,1945,1967]" captionTargetBox="[224,1359,234,1880]" captionTargetId="figure@23.[182,1404,195,1923]" captionTargetPageId="23" captionText="FIGURE 3. Anisepyris: aeneus species-group. Head in dorsal profile. A. A. amrasis sp. nov.; B. A. aradunakhori sp. nov.; C. A. arpharazoni sp. nov.; D. A. barahiris sp. nov.; E. A. barani sp. nov.; F. A.belegundi sp. nov.; G. A. belemiri sp. nov.; H. A. beregi sp. nov.; I. A. bereni sp. nov.; J. A.borladi sp. nov.; K. A.boromiri sp. nov.; L. A.borthandis sp. nov." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/1242269/files/figure.png" pageId="19" pageNumber="20">Figs 3H</figureCitation>
